PortSystem 1.0

name                    port_cutleaves
version                 0.1
categories              sysutils
platforms               darwin
maintainers             perry openmaintainer
description             Uninstall "leaves" - ports that have no dependents.
long_description        Inspired by FreeBSD's pkg_cutleaves, port_cutleaves \
                        is an interactive script that eases the \
                        uninstallation of "leaves" - ports that have no \
                        dependents.

homepage                http://svn.macports.org/repository/macports/contrib/port_cutleaves/files
